  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436110/extras/532313192fd7737ddaa6d9ad8856f2d4.avif?t=1733255535\" width=600 height=450 /></span><br><strong>KARNAL</strong> is a short atmospheric experience inspired by classic shooters from the 90's, with a modern twist.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436110/extras/7957aeeff3d12af97a1e8ef0a437969a.poster.avif?t=1733255535\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436110/extras/7957aeeff3d12af97a1e8ef0a437969a.webm?t=1733255535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436110/extras/7957aeeff3d12af97a1e8ef0a437969a.mp4?t=1733255535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You assume the role of an anonymous journalist, who finds himself in a scenario blurring the lines between nightmare and reality. Your objective is to escape confinement, return home, and ensure your wife's safety.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436110/extras/6729c412e7f33344bfb9adab4179c100.poster.avif?t=1733255535\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436110/extras/6729c412e7f33344bfb9adab4179c100.webm?t=1733255535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436110/extras/6729c412e7f33344bfb9adab4179c100.mp4?t=1733255535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>UNREAL ENGINE 5 LUMEN</strong> - This game was made using Unreal Engine 5, and uses Lumen for realistic global illumination & reflections.<br></li><li><strong>UNFORGIVING DIFFICULTY</strong> - You must master your movement and weapons, manage resources, and take advantage of your environment to get through everything the game throws at you.<br></li><li><strong>SECRETS & LOST TAPES</strong> - There are plenty of Easter Eggs for you to find, secrets within secrets, and the \"Lost Tapes\" side content.<br></li><li><strong>ARENA MODE</strong> - Save up money (or gamble) to purchase weapons and supplies, then battle endless waves of enemies in your arena of choice.</li></ul>",
